#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.26"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.26:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.26:0.2"
msgid "3. Puggalavagga"
msgstr "3. Persons"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.26:0.3"
msgid "26. Sevitabbasutta"
msgstr "26. Associates"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.125"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.26:1.1"
msgid "“Tayome, bhikkhave, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ."
msgstr "“These three people are found in the world."

msgctxt "an3.26:1.2"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.26:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atthi, bhikkhave, puggalo na sevitabbo na bhajitabbo na payirupāsitabbo."
msgstr "There is a person you shouldn’t associate with, accompany, or attend."

msgctxt "an3.26:1.4"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, puggalo sevitabbo bhajitabbo payirupāsitabbo."
msgstr "There is a person you should associate with, accompany, and attend."

msgctxt "an3.26:1.5"
msgid ""
"Atthi, bhikkhave, puggalo sakkatvā garuṃ katvā sevitabbo bhajitabbo "
"payirupāsitabbo."
msgstr ""
"There is a person you should associate with, accompany, and attend with "
"honor and respect."

msgctxt "an3.26:1.6"
msgid ""
"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, puggalo na sevitabbo na bhajitabbo na payirupāsitabbo?"
msgstr "Who is the person you shouldn’t associate with, accompany, or attend?"

msgctxt "an3.26:1.7"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo hīno hoti sīlena samādhinā paññāya."
msgstr "It’s someone who is inferior in terms of ethics, immersion, and wisdom."

msgctxt "an3.26:1.8"
msgid ""
"Evarūpo, bhikkhave, puggalo na sevitabbo na bhajitabbo na payirupāsitabbo "
"aññatra anuddayā aññatra anukampā."
msgstr ""
"You shouldn’t associate with, accompany, or attend such a person, except out "
"of kindness and compassion."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.26:2.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, puggalo sevitabbo bhajitabbo payirupāsitabbo?"
msgstr "Who is the person you should associate with, accompany, and attend?"

msgctxt "an3.26:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo sadiso hoti sīlena samādhinā paññāya."
msgstr "It’s someone who is similar in terms of ethics, immersion, and wisdom."

msgctxt "an3.26:2.3"
msgid "Evarūpo, bhikkhave, puggalo sevitabbo bhajitabbo payirupāsitabbo."
msgstr "You should associate with, accompany, and attend such a person."

msgctxt "an3.26:2.4"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

#. VAR: pavattinī → pavattanī (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an3.26:2.5"
msgid ""
"Sīlasāmaññagatānaṃ sataṃ sīlakathā ca no bhavissati, sā ca no pavattinī "
"bhavissati, sā ca no phāsu bhavissati."
msgstr ""
"Thinking, ‘Since our ethical conduct is similar, we can discuss ethics, the "
"conversation will flow, and we’ll both be at ease."

msgctxt "an3.26:2.6"
msgid ""
"Samādhisāmaññagatānaṃ sataṃ samādhikathā ca no bhavissati, sā ca no "
"pavattinī bhavissati, sā ca no phāsu bhavissati."
msgstr ""
"Since our immersion is similar, we can discuss immersion, the conversation "
"will flow, and we’ll both be at ease."

msgctxt "an3.26:2.7"
msgid ""
"Paññāsāmaññagatānaṃ sataṃ paññākathā ca no bhavissati, sā ca no pavattinī "
"bhavissati, sā ca no phāsu bhavissatīti."
msgstr ""
"Since our wisdom is similar, we can discuss wisdom, the conversation will "
"flow, and we’ll both be at ease.’"

msgctxt "an3.26:2.8"
msgid "Tasmā evarūpo puggalo sevitabbo bhajitabbo payirupāsitabbo."
msgstr ""
"That’s why you should associate with, accompany, and attend such a person."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.26:3.1"
msgid ""
"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, puggalo sakkatvā garuṃ katvā sevitabbo bhajitabbo "
"payirupāsitabbo?"
msgstr ""
"Who is the person you should associate with, accompany, and attend with "
"honor and respect?"

msgctxt "an3.26:3.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo adhiko hoti sīlena samādhinā paññāya."
msgstr "It’s someone who is superior in terms of ethics, immersion, and wisdom."

msgctxt "an3.26:3.3"
msgid ""
"Evarūpo, bhikkhave, puggalo sakkatvā garuṃ katvā sevitabbo bhajitabbo "
"payirupāsitabbo."
msgstr ""
"You should associate with, accompany, and attend such a person with honor "
"and respect."

msgctxt "an3.26:3.4"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

# BB has “in various respects” for tattha tattha, but this is too weak. It is an emphatic universal, as seen in https://suttacentral.net/pi/sn1.26 unlike the sun an moon, fire shines both day and night; https://suttacentral.net/pi/sn17.8 the mangu jackal is afflicted everywhere he goes; https://suttacentral.net/pi/thag2.32 dwellings are always impermanent; or https://suttacentral.net/pi/thag1.1, not having insight in various respects, but everywhere.
msgctxt "an3.26:3.5"
msgid ""
"Iti aparipūraṃ vā sīlakkhandhaṃ paripūressāmi, paripūraṃ vā sīlakkhandhaṃ "
"tattha tattha paññāya anuggahessāmi;"
msgstr ""
"Thinking, ‘I’ll fulfill the entire spectrum of ethical conduct I haven’t yet "
"fulfilled, or support with wisdom in every situation the ethical conduct I’"
"ve already fulfilled."

msgctxt "an3.26:3.6"
msgid ""
"aparipūraṃ vā samādhikkhandhaṃ paripūressāmi, paripūraṃ vā samādhikkhandhaṃ "
"tattha tattha paññāya anuggahessāmi;"
msgstr ""
"I’ll fulfill the entire spectrum of immersion I haven’t yet fulfilled, or "
"support with wisdom in every situation the immersion I’ve already fulfilled."

msgctxt "an3.26:3.7"
msgid ""
"aparipūraṃ vā paññākkhandhaṃ paripūressāmi, paripūraṃ vā paññākkhandhaṃ "
"tattha tattha paññāya anuggahessāmīti."
msgstr ""
"I’ll fulfill the entire spectrum of wisdom I haven’t yet fulfilled, or "
"support with wisdom in every situation the wisdom I’ve already fulfilled.’"

msgctxt "an3.26:3.8"
msgid ""
"Tasmā evarūpo puggalo sakkatvā garuṃ katvā sevitabbo bhajitabbo "
"payirupāsitabbo."
msgstr ""
"That’s why you should associate with, accompany, and attend this person with "
"honor and respect."

msgctxt "an3.26:3.9"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasminti."
msgstr "These are the three people found in the world.”"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.126"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an3.26:4.1"
msgid "Nihīyati puriso nihīnasevī,"
msgstr "“A man who associates with an inferior goes downhill,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.26:4.2"
msgid "Na ca hāyetha kadāci tulyasevī;"
msgstr "But associating with an equal, you’ll never decline;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.26:4.3"
msgid "Seṭṭhamupanamaṃ udeti khippaṃ,"
msgstr "Following the best, you’ll quickly rise up,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.26:4.4"
msgid "Tasmā attano uttariṃ bhajethā”ti."
msgstr "So you should keep company with people better than you.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.26:4.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
